DURATION:PT3H
SUMMARY:CodeRefinery Open House - Git masterclass
UID:88352aa6-a765-4953-a02b-efc8f853dc33@8835.org
DESCRIPTION:CodeRefinery Open House\n\nThis discussion is intended to see 
